Package org.sd.xml.record

Interface Summary
DivideStrategy Interface for defining a strategy to divide a record into subrecords.
 

Class Summary
DoubleBranchStrategy Divide strategy that identifies records where children of branching children branch.
DumpUtil Utility to dump records.
FilterStrategy A divide strategy that takes another divide strategy and filters the records.
HeterogeneousRecordChooser Choose records with the most diverse field patterns.
MultiBlockStrategy A record divide strategy for dividing a record where multiple blocks of consecutive fields exist and each block is a record.
PathHistogram Utility to use a histogram of paths to identify common paths.
PathHistogram.FieldGroupCollector  
PathHistogram.Path Container for a view of a record field suitable for use in a histogram.
Record Record abstraction holding attribute/value pairs, where each value can be another record or a string.
Record.Field Container for a terminal attribute/value pair.
Record.View Definition of a view strategy over a record.
RepeatingPatternDivideStrategy A top-down divide strategy where nodes containing a repeating pattern of tags are split.
Settings Class to parse xml settings files using the Record abstraction.
SplitStrategy A divide strategy to split a record when an attribute repeats.
TopDownDivideStrategy Base class for top-down divide strategies where all children of a node are considered to be records according to some rule.
Value A value is a terminal record holding data.
